<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="L" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Lead1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Lead,</orth> subst. the metal Plumbum: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.2.118" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 2, 118</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 3.60" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 60</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 3.60" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 60</bibl> <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.621" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 2, 621</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.2.33" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 2, 33</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.8" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.8" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 8</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.8" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 8</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.8" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 7, 8</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.20" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 9, 20</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.2.104" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 2, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.3.34" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 3, 34</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.48" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 7, 48</bibl>. Used for bullets: <bibl n="shak. lll 3.58" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 58</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 3.58" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL III, 58</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 1h4 5.3.35" default="NO" valid="yes">H4A V, 3, 35</bibl>. for coffins: <bibl n="shak. pp 396" default="NO" valid="yes">Pilgr. 396</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.7.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. II, 7, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 1.1.64" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A I, 1, 64</bibl>. in a molten state, for torments: <cit><quote>boiling in --s or oils,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 3.2.178" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. III, 2, 178</bibl></cit>. Emblem of heaviness: <bibl n="shak. ven 1072" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 1072</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.1.118" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 1, 118</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r3 5.3.152" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 V, 3, 152</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 1.1.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. I, 1, 184</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.1.186" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. I, 1, 186</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 1.4.15" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 15</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 2.5.17" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 5, 17</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 1, 6</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ant 3.11.72" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. III, 11, 72</bibl>. Plur. <emph>--s</emph> == a flat roof covered with lead: <bibl n="shak. r3 3.7.55" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 7, 55</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.1.227" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 1, 227</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 4.6.82" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 6, 82</bibl>.
